* Requirements

 * mono >= 2.4
 * mono-posix >= 2.4
 * mono-cairo >= 2.4
 * gstreamer >= 0.10.30
 * gnonlin >= 0.10.15
 * gtk-sharp >= 2.12
 * db40 >= 7.4


* Download
  LongoMatch source tarballs are available on gnome FTP:
   http://ftp.gnome.org/pub/GNOME/sources/longomatch/0.16/

  See the website for distribution-specific packages.

* Information and Feedback

 * Information for users and developers can be found on the LongoMatch website :
  http://www.longomatch.ylatuya.es/

 * Bugs and Features Requests
  http://bugzilla.gnome.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=longomatch


